As a traveler I have tried many budget friendly hotel like this one and it's great value for money, bed comfy, room it's not bad but 2 major things happen that won't stay at this hotel again;
1- a guy was smoking in the breakfast room while we are eating and no staff said anything !
2- at 6am another guest play a loud music while open her room door and wake up the whole isle and I repeat 6 am !! I thought the sound coming from the street as it was very loud ! I will definitely stay somewhere else next time
